OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFrequent showers through the
OL,6,Fmorning, with possible thunder.
OL,7,FShowers more scattered heading into
OL,8,Fthe afternoon with sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Rather windy, particularly
OL,10,Fnear coasts. Cool for the time of
OL,11,Fyear, but feeling warmer in the
OL,12,Fsunnier moments.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers becoming more
OL,15,Ffocussed towards the north and west
OL,16,Fthis evening and overnight, with some
OL,17,Fclear spells developing across the
OL,18,Fregion later in the night. Winds
OL,19,Fslowly easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
