OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FShowers are still likely in
OL,6,Fthe west on Friday, with more
OL,7,Fpersistent rain arriving here later.
OL,8,FVariable amounts of cloud elsewhere
OL,9,Fwith bright or sunny spells. Feeling
OL,10,Fcool for June.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWindy
OL,13,Fat first on Saturday with overnight
OL,14,Frain clearing to brighter skies later.
OL,15,FSunshine and showers on Sunday.
OL,16,FFurther rain Sunday night, ahead of a
OL,17,Fbrighter, showery day on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
